WEBVTT

00:00:50.780 --> 00:00:55.740
=Sugar and Lies=
(A Different Her: The Women's Trilogy)

00:00:56.820 --> 00:00:59.780
=Episode 16=
=The Daangerous Game of Heartbeats=

00:01:07.280 --> 00:01:08.120
Morning.

00:01:09.160 --> 00:01:10.000
You're up.

00:01:13.120 --> 00:01:14.000
Perfect timing.

00:01:14.000 --> 00:01:15.400
Let's add a few more clauses

00:01:15.640 --> 00:01:17.280
to the contract while we have breakfast.

00:01:17.600 --> 00:01:18.520
Clause One.

00:01:18.780 --> 00:01:20.000
Neither party shall interfere..

00:01:20.000 --> 00:01:21.560
Mrs. Yu,

00:01:21.560 --> 00:01:23.000
your work spirit took over again.

00:01:26.120 --> 00:01:27.760
Alright then, I'll set the first clause.

00:01:29.160 --> 00:01:30.520
During the contract period,

00:01:31.200 --> 00:01:32.040
Party B

00:01:32.960 --> 00:01:33.800
shall not

00:01:34.200 --> 00:01:36.600
have close contact with any man
other than Party A

00:01:36.600 --> 00:01:37.440
or engage in

00:01:38.760 --> 00:01:40.160
unnecessary physical touch,

00:01:40.160 --> 00:01:41.920
such as but not limited to

00:01:42.600 --> 00:01:44.080
pulling or tugging,

00:01:44.080 --> 00:01:45.160
or arms around shoulders.

00:01:47.680 --> 00:01:48.520
Keep going.

00:01:48.640 --> 00:01:49.480
Also,

00:02:01.360 --> 00:02:02.880
don't mess with each other's stuff.

00:02:13.160 --> 00:02:14.000
No problem.

00:02:15.520 --> 00:02:16.360
Then let's hope

00:02:16.360 --> 00:02:18.040
we both stick to the deal.

00:02:25.040 --> 00:02:25.880
Mr. Yu.

00:02:26.320 --> 00:02:27.800
Better take care of yourself first.

00:02:39.760 --> 00:02:41.920
My brother's been watching me
closely lately.

00:02:41.920 --> 00:02:43.200
The way he looks at me

00:02:43.200 --> 00:02:44.520
feels off.

00:02:45.120 --> 00:02:46.920
If he finds out we're together,

00:02:47.600 --> 00:02:48.440
I'm scared that...

00:02:48.680 --> 00:02:49.520
Miaomiao,

00:02:50.320 --> 00:02:51.440
don't be.

00:02:51.920 --> 00:02:52.880
I'll keep you safe.

00:02:53.880 --> 00:02:54.800
Besides,

00:02:55.280 --> 00:02:56.640
your brother's attention right now

00:02:57.800 --> 00:02:59.520
is mostly on Ding Daang.

00:03:00.440 --> 00:03:01.760
The little bit that's left

00:03:02.440 --> 00:03:03.600
was all given to Keep Love.

00:03:04.850 --> 00:03:06.050
Does that mean we don't have to

00:03:06.050 --> 00:03:07.250
keep hiding like this anymore?

00:03:08.160 --> 00:03:09.640
We can finally be together openly.

00:03:11.800 --> 00:03:12.640
Trust me,

00:03:13.720 --> 00:03:14.840
our good days

00:03:16.080 --> 00:03:17.120
are ahead of us.

00:03:22.560 --> 00:03:23.840
Miaomiao, remember,

00:03:25.440 --> 00:03:26.780
don't go soft at crucial moments.

00:03:28.120 --> 00:03:29.200
When it's time to be tough,

00:03:29.800 --> 00:03:30.640
be a little tougher.

00:03:35.480 --> 00:03:36.840
It's all for our own good.

00:03:39.680 --> 00:03:40.520
Got it,

00:03:41.000 --> 00:03:41.840
Mr. Hu.

00:03:56.960 --> 00:03:58.160
Did you read the script yet?

00:03:58.400 --> 00:03:59.240
Sorry,

00:03:59.760 --> 00:04:00.800
I'm doing this alone today.

00:04:02.320 --> 00:04:03.480
What do you mean by that?

00:04:03.720 --> 00:04:05.440
He means he's hosting it alone.

00:04:07.760 --> 00:04:09.520
Zhou Haoran, I'm talking to you.

00:04:09.920 --> 00:04:10.840
Cat got your tongue?

00:04:14.800 --> 00:04:16.080
I've got something official

00:04:17.360 --> 00:04:18.240
to tell you,

00:04:19.240 --> 00:04:20.080
you're fired.

00:04:23.480 --> 00:04:24.520
You're firing me?

00:04:25.280 --> 00:04:26.120
Why?

00:04:26.440 --> 00:04:27.280
No reason.

00:04:27.480 --> 00:04:28.520
Zhou Haoran,

00:04:29.200 --> 00:04:31.120
you're just scared I'll outshine you.

00:04:31.560 --> 00:04:32.840
Burning bridges now, huh?

00:04:35.440 --> 00:04:36.400
Maimai, calm down.

00:04:36.400 --> 00:04:37.600
That's exactly what he means.

00:04:37.880 --> 00:04:38.720
Fine.

00:04:39.160 --> 00:04:40.000
Zhou Haoran,

00:04:41.120 --> 00:04:42.320
you just wait and see.

00:04:52.700 --> 00:04:53.560
With or without love,

00:04:53.560 --> 00:04:54.440
just follow your heart

00:04:54.440 --> 00:04:55.400
and say it out loud.

00:04:55.680 --> 00:04:56.650
Just be straightforward.

00:04:59.460 --> 00:05:01.180
(Suga Love)

00:05:07.480 --> 00:05:08.960
The cake didn't offend you, did it?

00:05:11.920 --> 00:05:12.760
What's up?

00:05:13.040 --> 00:05:14.000
Feeling down?

00:05:17.840 --> 00:05:20.360
I know Yu Kun forced him into it,

00:05:21.240 --> 00:05:24.480
but he acted completely cold.

00:05:26.080 --> 00:05:27.800
You know it was just an act.

00:05:27.800 --> 00:05:29.280
So why get upset?

00:05:29.840 --> 00:05:31.880
He's just Yu Kun's lapdog

00:05:32.360 --> 00:05:33.960
and bites whoever Yu Kun points at.

00:05:35.000 --> 00:05:35.840
Let me tell you,

00:05:36.960 --> 00:05:38.160
I've finally figured it out.

00:05:39.040 --> 00:05:40.720
Men are all the same—none worth trusting.

00:05:43.600 --> 00:05:44.840
You only realized that now?

00:05:45.520 --> 00:05:46.360
Here.

00:05:46.480 --> 00:05:48.480
Have some cake
to heal your hurt feelings.

00:05:48.600 --> 00:05:49.880
Get your mood back on track.

00:05:52.360 --> 00:05:53.680
Received by Miss Gu.

00:05:53.680 --> 00:05:55.520
Special delivery from Mr. Zhou.

00:05:56.200 --> 00:05:57.040
Refused.

00:05:57.600 --> 00:05:59.000
Mr. Zhou said,

00:05:59.000 --> 00:06:00.000
it's pretty pricey.

00:06:00.000 --> 00:06:01.400
So maybe don't turn it down.

00:06:01.400 --> 00:06:03.560
You can always resell it online later.

00:06:06.760 --> 00:06:09.680
Looks like
someone hit your soft spot again.

00:06:09.880 --> 00:06:11.200
Did he?

00:06:12.280 --> 00:06:13.560
Not a chance.

00:06:18.320 --> 00:06:19.160
President Yu.

00:06:22.960 --> 00:06:24.320
Mr. Steven

00:06:24.320 --> 00:06:25.360
is still confident

00:06:25.360 --> 00:06:26.680
about Keep Love's growth.

00:06:27.080 --> 00:06:29.080
He heard about
that small incident last time,

00:06:30.080 --> 00:06:31.200
but thinks it's no big deal.

00:06:32.720 --> 00:06:33.960
Please thank him

00:06:33.960 --> 00:06:35.480
for his kind support.

00:06:36.720 --> 00:06:38.920
But recently, Keep Love

00:06:39.440 --> 00:06:40.720
has been running smoothly.

00:06:41.640 --> 00:06:42.840
Our funding is steady.

00:06:43.760 --> 00:06:45.320
We don't need extra investment for now.

00:06:45.960 --> 00:06:46.800
Good.

00:06:48.360 --> 00:06:49.960
President Yu, you seem pretty confident.

00:06:50.600 --> 00:06:52.520
Is it because of Miss Ding Daang's

00:06:53.520 --> 00:06:54.520
substantial

00:06:55.280 --> 00:06:56.200
inheritance, right?

00:07:00.000 --> 00:07:00.840
But you know,

00:07:01.680 --> 00:07:02.720
before the money's in hand,

00:07:03.200 --> 00:07:04.400
things can still change.

00:07:13.360 --> 00:07:14.360
I've passed the message.

00:07:15.240 --> 00:07:16.960
President Yu, think it over again.

00:07:17.480 --> 00:07:19.120
Mr. Steven's offer is sincere.

00:07:21.360 --> 00:07:22.200
I'll take my leave.

00:07:36.480 --> 00:07:37.480
Boss, stay calm.

00:07:37.800 --> 00:07:39.260
Hu Yitong is here to stir things up.

00:07:39.260 --> 00:07:40.840
Ding Daang is just a piece
in your plan.

00:07:40.840 --> 00:07:41.800
Mind your own business.

00:07:59.120 --> 00:08:00.560
I'm your partner,

00:08:00.800 --> 00:08:02.120
not some servant you hired.

00:08:02.320 --> 00:08:04.040
Can't you put away your own clothes?

00:08:05.280 --> 00:08:06.400
I never asked you to.

00:08:08.760 --> 00:08:09.800
But then again,

00:08:12.440 --> 00:08:13.400
a couple is one unit.

00:08:13.640 --> 00:08:14.480
Mrs. Yu.

00:08:15.280 --> 00:08:17.120
It doesn't matter who does them.

00:08:17.680 --> 00:08:19.600
Drawing too many lines hurts feelings.

00:08:20.520 --> 00:08:21.360
Alright.

00:08:23.160 --> 00:08:24.160
Put them away yourself.

00:08:24.480 --> 00:08:25.680
I'm heading out.

00:08:26.040 --> 00:08:26.880
Where are you going?

00:08:28.680 --> 00:08:29.840
Clause two of the contract.

00:08:30.520 --> 00:08:31.640
Both parties

00:08:31.640 --> 00:08:33.840
shall not interfere
in each other's private life,

00:08:34.240 --> 00:08:35.080
including

00:08:35.080 --> 00:08:37.200
work, emotions, and social life.

00:08:38.200 --> 00:08:39.200
You're not allowed to go.

00:08:40.080 --> 00:08:40.920
Why not?

00:08:44.880 --> 00:08:46.680
Clause three of the contract,

00:08:48.960 --> 00:08:50.000
during the contract period,

00:08:50.720 --> 00:08:52.920
each must give emotional support
to the other.

00:08:54.800 --> 00:08:55.640
So what then?

00:08:56.440 --> 00:08:57.320
I ordered dinner.

00:08:57.320 --> 00:08:58.680
Your favorite Hunan dishes.

00:08:58.680 --> 00:08:59.760
It's for two. Stay.

00:08:59.760 --> 00:09:00.640
Or it'll go to waste.

00:09:01.880 --> 00:09:03.000
What if I say no?

00:09:09.040 --> 00:09:10.040
Then it's a breach.

00:09:12.840 --> 00:09:13.800
Shameless.

00:09:21.760 --> 00:09:22.600
Mrs. Yu.

00:09:24.120 --> 00:09:25.440
So eager to throw yourself at me?

00:09:30.960 --> 00:09:32.120
I'm going to change now.

00:09:36.960 --> 00:09:37.880
Don't follow me.

00:09:43.100 --> 00:09:44.500
It's not like I haven't seen before.

00:10:06.160 --> 00:10:07.760
Clause five: separate rooms.

00:10:07.760 --> 00:10:08.800
Go back to your own room.

00:10:11.200 --> 00:10:12.200
Miss Ding.

00:10:13.040 --> 00:10:15.440
This big house of yours feels so empty.

00:10:16.400 --> 00:10:17.280
Only this room

00:10:17.880 --> 00:10:19.920
is warm
and actually interesting to stay in.

00:10:20.280 --> 00:10:21.240
My favorite room.

00:10:26.040 --> 00:10:26.880
Let me remind you,

00:10:27.360 --> 00:10:28.300
you broke the contract.

00:10:43.920 --> 00:10:45.440
Go back to your room right now.

00:10:46.720 --> 00:10:47.660
How much is the penalty?

00:10:48.120 --> 00:10:49.280
I'll pay double.

00:10:53.080 --> 00:10:54.120
It's really expensive.

00:10:57.560 --> 00:10:59.480
Everything has a price, doesn't it?

00:11:03.040 --> 00:11:03.880
It's priceless.

00:11:16.240 --> 00:11:17.280
What are you looking at?

00:11:21.240 --> 00:11:22.440
I'm trying to see

00:11:22.880 --> 00:11:24.360
how thick your skin is.

00:11:27.440 --> 00:11:28.520
Your ear

00:11:29.440 --> 00:11:30.280
is turning red.

00:11:44.320 --> 00:11:45.990
I still want to break the contract tonight.

00:11:48.200 --> 00:11:49.040
Just one last time.

00:11:50.240 --> 00:11:51.080
Alright?

00:11:55.880 --> 00:11:56.720
No way.

00:12:02.800 --> 00:12:03.640
Remember,

00:12:05.080 --> 00:12:07.360
doing as you're told
is your only option.

00:12:08.640 --> 00:12:09.480
Otherwise…

00:12:12.240 --> 00:12:13.920
I've got plenty of ways
to deal with you.

00:12:16.560 --> 00:12:17.440
Why didn't you tell me

00:12:17.440 --> 00:12:19.000
about Hu Yitong and Miaomiao's meeting.

00:12:21.720 --> 00:12:22.560
Boss.

00:12:22.960 --> 00:12:25.040
Maybe Miaomiao has her own plan.

00:12:25.440 --> 00:12:26.400
Once we finish this job,

00:12:27.400 --> 00:12:28.520
we'll leave Mancheng.

00:12:29.160 --> 00:12:30.200
I want to stay.

00:12:30.200 --> 00:12:32.000
(Warning)
Ding Daang was in an accident.

00:12:56.860 --> 00:13:03.860
♪I forgot this is a movie meant for one♪

00:13:08.260 --> 00:13:15.620
♪Somehow you're still here,
crying with me♪

00:13:20.070 --> 00:13:22.010
♪They say♪

00:13:22.420 --> 00:13:30.800
♪Lovers should never hold hands
while watching a sad movie♪

00:13:31.320 --> 00:13:34.300
♪Some endings cannot be changed♪

00:13:34.520 --> 00:13:40.470
♪They don't belong in sweet memories♪

00:13:41.850 --> 00:13:47.610
♪I've already lost you♪

00:13:47.610 --> 00:13:53.090
♪Thinking of it takes my breath away♪

00:13:53.390 --> 00:13:59.340
♪The movie ends, so many couples around♪

00:13:59.340 --> 00:14:04.120
♪Yet none were ever like us♪

00:14:05.230 --> 00:14:09.260
♪The past will always pass♪

00:14:09.590 --> 00:14:17.170
♪If you could still hold me tight
in your arms♪

00:14:17.640 --> 00:14:20.890
♪I'd believe
that there are miracles in love♪

00:14:21.450 --> 00:14:27.100
♪I'd prove
that I'm still in love with you♪

00:14:29.560 --> 00:14:33.090
♪I've learned how to cherish
what we had♪

00:14:33.090 --> 00:14:39.350
♪But sadly, it's not you♪